- You can obtain a Azure Subscibtion one of the folow ways:
  - Enterpise Agreement
    - A client is willing to up front pay for Azure can include Azure in their contract. Utilising any number of the several cloud services that Azure provides allows you to use the commitment throughout the course of the whole year.
  - Personal Free account
    - Any user can sign up,  and get started using Azure right away, and you won't be charged until you choose to upgrade
  - Microsoft Partner
    - They can design and implement your Azure cloud solution, also they have the business and technology expertise to recommend solutions that meet the unique needs of your business.
  - Microsoft Reseller
    - Buy Azure through the Open Licensing program, which provides a simple, flexible way to purchase cloud services.
